ge but fixed values of\n$\\lambda$, these differences are found to increase like the inverse of the\nbinding radius.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2013 20:45:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jan 2013 23:51:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-23"}
