Q}_{D}$. When $D$ is even (resp. odd) we show\nthat actions of the adjacency, dual adjacency and weighted adjacency matrices\nfor $Q_{D}$ (resp. $\\tilde{Q}_{D}$) on any irreducible $T$-module (resp.\n$\\tilde{T}$-module) form a totally bipartite (resp. almost bipartite) Leonard\ntriple of Bannai/Ito type and classify the Leonard triple up to isomorphism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2013 00:24:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-07"}
